      <div class="Section3"><a name="_conformance_class_abstract_test_suite_normative" id="_conformance_class_abstract_test_suite_normative"></a>
        <h1 class="Annex"><b>Annex A</b><br/>(normative) <br/><b>Conformance Class Abstract Test Suite (Normative)</b></h1>
        <div class="Note"><a name="_7fe1b011-f935-414c-81d4-2664bf73f6f7" id="_7fe1b011-f935-414c-81d4-2664bf73f6f7"></a>
          <p class="Note"><span class="note_label">NOTE</span><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Ensure that there is a conformance class for each requirements class and a test for each requirement (identified by requirement name and number)</p>
        </div>
